      <abstract>
        <p>April 3 article about plan by New York City Department of Correction to reopen Brooklyn House of Detention referred incorrectly to community leader who opposes reopening; Sandy Balboza is woman</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on April 3 about a plan by the New York City Department of Correction to reopen and expand the Brooklyn House of Detention in Boerum Hill referred incorrectly to a community leader who opposes the reopening. Sandy Balboza, president of the Atlantic Avenue Betterment Association, is a woman.</p>
      </block>
